title: Excel VBA (macros)
text:
Sort tasks

#| highlight-style: none

Option Explicit

'===========================================================
'====> Sort tasks according to status and priority
'===========================================================

Sub Sort_Tasks()

'Define the variables
Dim rng_data As Range
Dim rng_key1 As Range
Dim rng_key2 As Range

'Set the variables
Set rng_data = Range("E2:J100000")
Set rng_key1 = Range("H2")
Set rng_key2 = Range("G2")

'Perform the Sort
rng_data.Sort key1:=rng_key1, key2:=rng_key2, Header:=xlYes

End Sub
